---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import DoubleHeight from '../../components/teletext/DoubleHeight.astro';
import Separator from '../../components/teletext/Separator.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="AR City Exploration"
  description="Master's thesis blending augmented reality with storytelling for an immersive exploration of Frankfurt."
  pageNumber="203"
  headerBg="bg-teletext-green"
  headerText="text-teletext-black"
>
  <article>
    <section class="mb-[2ch]">
      <DoubleHeight as="h1" color="text-teletext-yellow">AR City Exploration</DoubleHeight>
      <p class="text-teletext-cyan mt-[1ch]">
        Finding a new approach for location-based storytelling in AR.
      </p>
      <p class="text-teletext-white/60 text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">(Archive)</p>
    </section>

    <img src="/img/arCityExploration/raubkunst_cover.gif" alt="Raubkunst AR experience cover" class="w-full mb-[2ch]" loading="lazy" />

    <Separator color="text-teletext-green" char="─" />

    <section class="my-[2ch]">
      <h2 class="text-teletext-yellow font-bold mb-[1ch]">Key Points</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-[2ch]">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-teletext-cyan font-bold mb-[0.5ch]">Activities</h3>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-[0.5ch]">
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Guerilla usability testing</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Unity3D + AR prototyping</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Academic Research</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Experience & Story Design</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Sound Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-teletext-cyan font-bold mb-[0.5ch]">Deliverables</h3>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-[0.5ch]">
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Proof-of-Concept</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> iOS Application</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Conceptual Framework</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Public Presentations</li>
            <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Master Thesis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="my-[2ch]">
      <h2 class="text-teletext-yellow font-bold mb-[1ch]">Outcome</h2>
      <p class="mb-[1ch]">
        We created a holistic experience concept bringing together transmedia storytelling, interactive technology, and real places. We also built a promising conceptual framework (Memorama) for explorative AR experiences and an iOS prototype to showcase its application.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="my-[2ch]">
      <h2 class="text-teletext-yellow font-bold mb-[1ch]">Discovery & Design</h2>
      <p class="mb-[1ch]">
        Applied Design Thinking methods throughout: semantic analysis, 10-plus-10s, ad hoc workshops. Used a physical research wall to align on findings. Created feasibility maps, personas, and stakeholder maps.
      </p>
      <figure class="my-[2ch]">
        <img src="/img/arCityExploration/raubkunst_feasibilityMatrix.jpg" alt="Feasibility matrix for design decisions" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="text-teletext-green text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">
          Feasibility matrix for deciding what to build.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="my-[2ch]">
        <img src="/img/arCityExploration/raubkunst_guerilla_testing.jpg" alt="User testing AR at a Frankfurt monument" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="text-teletext-green text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">
          Guerilla testing: a participant triggers an AR installation at a Frankfurt monument.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="my-[2ch]">
      <h2 class="text-teletext-yellow font-bold mb-[1ch]">Experience Design</h2>
      <p class="mb-[1ch]">
        Every design decision was intentional. We chose a starting place with nearby cafes, used vibration for haptic feedback, kept sound design blending into the environment, and reminded users to take breaks at local stores.
      </p>
      <figure class="my-[2ch]">
        <img src="/img/arCityExploration/raubkunst_experience_design_principles.webp" alt="Experience Design Principles" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="text-teletext-green text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">
          Experience Design Principles for Raubkunst.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="my-[2ch]">
      <h2 class="text-teletext-yellow font-bold mb-[1ch]">Memorama Framework</h2>
      <p class="mb-[1ch]">
        A conceptual framework for location-based experiences that combine fiction, historical knowledge, and contemporary technology. Three abstract spaces: Navigation Spaces, Discovery Spaces, and the Home Space.
      </p>
      <figure class="my-[2ch]">
        <img src="/img/arCityExploration/raubkunst_memorama.png" alt="Memorama Framework diagram" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="text-teletext-green text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">
          The Memorama Framework.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="my-[2ch]">
      <h2 class="text-teletext-yellow font-bold mb-[1ch]">Prototype</h2>
      <figure class="my-[2ch]">
        <img src="/img/arCityExploration/raubkunst_appscreens.webp" alt="Raubkunst app screens" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="text-teletext-green text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">
          App screens for the Raubkunst prototype.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <p class="mb-[1ch]">
        Built with Unity3D and Vuforia. Partnered with a fellow UX Developer to create scenes and test image trigger recognition, story triggers, and object positioning.
      </p>

      <!-- YouTube: Story Introduction -->
      <figure class="my-[2ch]">
        <div class="aspect-video">
          <iframe
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sccf2EZheEw"
            title="Story Introduction AR Installation"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
            class="border border-teletext-white/20"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-teletext-green text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">
          AR installation that can be triggered anywhere.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <!-- YouTube: Navigation Experience -->
      <figure class="my-[2ch]">
        <div class="aspect-video">
          <iframe
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zotKldUVY_w"
            title="Navigation Experience Prototype"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
            class="border border-teletext-white/20"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <figcaption class="text-teletext-green text-teletext-sm mt-[0.5ch]">
          Navigation Experience Prototype.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="my-[2ch]">
      <h2 class="text-teletext-yellow font-bold mb-[1ch]">Outcomes</h2>
      <ul class="list-none space-y-[0.5ch]">
        <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Presented at Frankfurt Book Fair 2018</li>
        <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Deepened skills in Unity3D and Interaction Design</li>
        <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Demonstrated impact of great team chemistry</li>
        <li><span class="text-teletext-green">▸</span> Led to career opportunities for all team members</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <Separator color="text-teletext-green" char="─" />

    <nav class="mt-[2ch]">
      <a href="/projects/" class="text-teletext-cyan hover:text-teletext-yellow">← Back to Projects</a>
    </nav>
  </article>
</PageLayout>
